{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775840048241,"sessionID":"ses_287b0697fffeFV5WufzVgc4r65","part":{"id":"prt_d785045b8001H8CF8PGkHt2sDc","messageID":"msg_d78501be50015GAn8ORAf7wHQN","sessionID":"ses_287b0697fffeFV5WufzVgc4r65","type":"tool","tool":"edit","callID":"toolu_62d7d85b7c9c4267812d000c","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-002/delta-spec.md","newString":"# Delta Spec: AR-002 — CRD CodeInterpreter 类型定义\n\n## Overview\n\nThis delta-spec defines acceptance scenarios for implementing the CodeInterpreter CRD type definitions in `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1`.\n\n## Base Specifications\n\n- **AR**: AR-002\n- **Module**: `pkg/apis`\n- **Language**: Go\n- **Size**: S\n- **Base Spec**: `deployment/client-go.md` (client-go library types)\n\n---\n\n## Scenario: CodeInterpreter Type Definition\n\n### AR-002-001: CodeInterpreter type definition\n\n- **GIVEN** a Go package at `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1`\n- **WHEN** defining `CodeInterpreter` struct with kubebuilder markers\n- **THEN** the type SHALL embed `metav1.TypeMeta` with `json:\",inline\"` tag\n- **AND** SHALL embed `metav1.ObjectMeta` with `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"` tag\n- **AND** SHALL include `Spec` field of type `CodeInterpreterSpec` with `json:\"spec,omitempty\"` tag\n- **AND** SHALL include `Status` field of type `CodeInterpreterStatus` with `json:\"status,omitempty\"` tag\n- **AND** SHALL have `+genclient` marker\n- **AND** SHALL have `+kubebuilder:object:root=true` marker\n- **AND** SHALL have `+kubebuilder:subresource:status` marker\n- **AND** SHALL have `+kubebuilder:resource:shortName=ci` marker\n\n### AR-002-002: CodeInterpreterList type definition\n\n- **GIVEN** `CodeInterpreter` type is defined\n- **WHEN** defining `CodeInterpreterList` struct\n- **THEN** the type SHALL embed `metav1.TypeMeta` with `json:\",inline\"` tag\n- **AND** SHALL embed `metav1.ListMeta` with `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"` tag\n- **AND** SHALL include `Items` field of type `[]CodeInterpreter` with `json:\"items\"` tag\n- **AND** SHALL have `+kubebuilder:object:root=true` marker\n\n### AR-002-003: CodeInterpreterSpec fields\n\n- **GIVEN** `CodeInterpreterSpec` struct definition\n- **WHEN** defining spec fields\n- **THEN** `AuthMode` SHALL be of type `AuthMode` (enum: \"picod\", \"none\"), optional, default `\"picod\"`\n- **AND** `MaxSessionDuration` SHALL be `string` type, optional, default `\"8h\"`\n- **AND** `SessionTimeout` SHALL be `string` type, optional, default `\"15m\"`\n- **AND** `Ports` SHALL be `[]TargetPort` type, optional\n- **AND** `Template` SHALL be of type `ContainerTemplateSpec`, required\n- **AND** `WarmPoolSize` SHALL be `int32` type, optional, default `0`\n\n### AR-002-004: CodeInterpreterStatus with ready field\n\n- **GIVEN** `CodeInterpreterStatus` struct definition\n- **WHEN** defining status subresource\n- **THEN** it SHALL include `Conditions` of type `[]metav1.Condition` with `json:\"conditions,omitempty\"` tag\n- **AND** SHALL include `ObservedGeneration` of type `int64` with `json:\"observedGeneration,omitempty\"` tag\n- **AND** SHALL include `Ready` of type `bool` with `json:\"ready\"` tag\n\n### AR-002-005: Supporting types definition\n\n- **GIVEN** CodeInterpreter types are defined\n- **WHEN** defining supporting types\n- **THEN** `TargetPort` SHALL include `Port` (int32), `Protocol` (HTTP/HTTPS), `Name`, `PathPrefix` fields\n- **AND** `ContainerTemplateSpec` SHALL include `Image` (required), `Command`, `Args`, `Env`, `Resources`, `RuntimeClassName` fields\n- **AND** `AuthMode` SHALL be defined as a string type with constants `AuthModePicod` and `AuthModeNone`\n\n### AR-002-006: DeepCopy method generation\n\n- **GIVEN** CodeInterpreter types are defined in `types.go`\n- **WHEN** running deepcopy generation\n- **THEN** `CodeInterpreter.DeepCopyInto(*CodeInterpreter)` SHALL be generated\n- **AND** `CodeInterpreter.DeepCopy() *CodeInterpreter` SHALL be generated\n- **AND** `CodeInterpreter.DeepCopyObject() runtime.Object` SHALL be generated\n- **AND** `CodeInterpreterList.DeepCopyInto(*CodeInterpreterList)` SHALL be generated\n- **AND** `CodeInterpreterList.DeepCopy() *CodeInterpreterList` SHALL be generated\n- **AND** `CodeInterpreterList.DeepCopyObject() runtime.Object` SHALL be generated\n- **AND** `CodeInterpreterSpec.DeepCopyInto(*CodeInterpreterSpec)` SHALL be generated\n- **AND** `CodeInterpreterSpec.DeepCopy() *CodeInterpreterSpec` SHALL be generated\n- **AND** `CodeInterpreterStatus.DeepCopyInto(*CodeInterpreterStatus)` SHALL be generated\n- **AND** `CodeInterpreterStatus.DeepCopy() *CodeInterpreterStatus` SHALL be generated\n\n---\n\n## References\n\n- Base spec: `deployment/client-go.md`\n- AR-001: CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义\n- API Group: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh`\n- Version: `v1alpha1`","oldString":"# Delta Spec: AR-002 — CRD CodeInterpreter 类型定义\n\n## Overview\n\nThis delta-spec defines acceptance scenarios for implementing the CodeInterpreter CRD type definitions in `pkg/apis`.\n\n## Base Specifications\n\n- **AR**: AR-002\n- **Module**: `pkg/apis`\n- **Language**: Go\n- **Size**: S\n- **Base Spec**: `deployment/client-go.md` (client-go library types)\n\n---\n\n## Scenario: CodeInterpreter Type Definition\n\n### AR-002-001: CodeInterpreter type definition\n\n- **GIVEN** a Go package at `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1`\n- **WHEN** defining `CodeInterpreter` struct with kubebuilder markers\n- **THEN** the type SHALL embed `metav1.TypeMeta` and `metav1.ObjectMeta`\n- **AND** SHALL include `Spec` field of type `CodeInterpreterSpec`\n- **AND** SHALL include `Status` field of type `CodeInterpreterStatus`\n\n### AR-002-002: CodeInterpreterSpec fields\n\n- **GIVEN** `CodeInterpreterSpec` struct definition\n- **WHEN** defining spec fields\n- **THEN** `AuthMode` SHALL be of type `AuthMode` (enum: \"picod\", \"none\"), optional, default `\"picod\"`\n- **AND** `MaxSessionDuration` SHALL be `string` type,