yInto(*CodeInterpreterList)` SHALL be generated\n- **AND** `CodeInterpreterList.DeepCopy() *CodeInterpreterList` SHALL be generated\n- **AND** `CodeInterpreterList.DeepCopyObject() runtime.Object` SHALL be generated\n- **AND** `CodeInterpreterSpec.DeepCopyInto(*CodeInterpreterSpec)` SHALL be generated\n- **AND** `CodeInterpreterSpec.DeepCopy() *CodeInterpreterSpec` SHALL be generated\n- **AND** `CodeInterpreterStatus.DeepCopyInto(*CodeInterpreterStatus)` SHALL be generated\n- **AND** `CodeInterpreterStatus.DeepCopy() *CodeInterpreterStatus` SHALL be generated\n\n---\n\n## References\n\n- Base spec: `deployment/client-go.md`\n- AR-001: CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义\n- API Group: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh`\n- Version: `v1alpha1`","additions":46,"deletions":9},"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-002/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775840048213,"end":1775840048238}}}}
